properties.abstract: The «Gantrisch Bike-Panoramaweg» is considered a beginners tour in the Gantrisch Biking portfolio and allows plenty of time to enjoy the beautiful scenery.
properties.description:
Besides Ottenleubad, the Panorama Round Tour can also begin by the Gurnigel Berghaus guesthouse, Gurnigel Wasserscheide or in Schwarzenbühl/Selital. But it makes no odds where you begin - this easy route turns everyone into a bike fan.

With relatively few metres in altitude to climb (from 1470 to 1600) and smooth and steady up and down ride, the Panorama Route not only earns its name, but allows plenty of time to stop and see. The route comprises all sorts of biking trails; the majority of which compact woodland trails or gravel paths. Guest houses and transport stops along this easy round tour add to the pleasure, with plenty of food and refreshments for healthy appetites.
